    • evaluate

      public int evaluate(DEProblem probl, int num_eval)
      Re-evaluates this individuals fitness with the problems fitness function.
      Parameters:
      probl - Optimization problem to be evaluated.
      num_eval - Tail recursive parameter for how many individuals evaluated.
      Returns:
      Return num_eval+1 as in tail recursion.
